    "\n",
    "## Key rules to carry forward\n",
    "\n",
    "1. **Iterate directly** — never `for i in range(len(list))`\n",
    "2. **Comprehensions over loops** — but keep them readable\n",
    "3. **`**kwargs` is everywhere** — especially in AI libraries\n",
    "4. **Empty collections are falsy** — use `if not users:` not `if len(users) == 0:`\n",
    "5. **`self` is not magic** — it's just \"which instance am I?\"\n",
